OL,5, Huw Edwards is in hospital with        
OL,6, "serious mental health issues", his    
OL,7, wife says, as she named him as the BBC 
OL,8, presenter at the centre of allegations.
OL,10,FHis wife Vicky Flind said she was      
OL,11,Fissuing a statement on his behalf after
OL,12,Fdays of speculation "primarily out of  
OL,13,Fconcern for his mental well-being and  
OL,14,Fto protect our children".              
OL,16,FThe Sun has claimed he paid a young    
OL,17,Fperson for sexually explicit images.   
OL,19,FThe Met Police says Edwards, 61, will  
OL,20,Fnot face any police action.            
